snippet.title: Which Country Has the Bigger Population Geography Quiz!
snippet.description:
In today’s video, I’m going to be revisiting the classic higher or lower population quiz and attempting to correctly identify the larger population as many times in a row as I can. Play along and see if you can beat me!

Play the quiz here: https://moreorless.io/game/population-by-country
